      <p class="text-slate-500 mb-8">Last updated: January 1, 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
          By accessing and using StockTheEvent, you accept and agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our service.
        </p>

