          StockTheEvent provides drink quantity calculators and planning tools for events. Our calculations are based on industry standards and are intended as estimates only.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
