          <li>We are not responsible for over-purchasing or under-purchasing</li>
          <li>Results should be used as a starting point, not absolute guidance</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">Responsible Drinking</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
          StockTheEvent promotes responsible alcohol consumption. By using our service, you confirm that:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>You are of legal drinking age in your jurisdiction</li>
          <li>You will serve alcohol responsibly at your events</li>
          <li>You understand the risks associated with alcohol consumption</li>
          <li>You will comply with all local laws regarding alcohol service</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">Affiliate Links</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
          Our site contains affiliate links to Amazon and other retailers. When you click these links and make a purchase, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you. This helps support our free calculator service.
        </p>

